@startuml
title Activity Diagram - View Course Content

start

note right
Steps:
1. User opens a course
2. System validates access (enrollment/role)
3. If access granted, system loads modules and content list
4. User selects a content item
5. System displays content OR access denied message
end note

:Open Course;
:Validate Access;

if (Access granted?) then (Yes)
  :Load Modules and Content List;
  :Select Content Item;
  :Display Content;
else (No)
  :Show Access Denied;
endif

stop
@enduml
